{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_70","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve got the root cause now. The XML test is not failing inside the `OpenTelemetryAppender` path at all: log4j never switches to XML configuration because `PluginRegistry` can’t load `org.apache.logging.log4j.core.config.xml.XmlConfigurationFactory` from the plugin cache at runtime, so it falls back to `DefaultConfiguration`. That means the missing metadata is for log4j’s dynamically loaded configuration-factory plugin classes, not for the appender builder."}}
